    <h2 class="h4 card-title">Search tips</h2>
    <ul class="advanced-help">

     <li>Use quotation marks to search as a phrase.

     </li><li>Use "+" before a term to make it required. (Otherwise results matching only some of your terms may be included).</li>

     <li>Use "-" before a word or phrase to exclude.

     </li><li>Use "OR", "AND", and "NOT" to create complex boolean logic. You can use parentheses in your complex expressions. </li>
     <li>Truncation and wildcards are not supported - word-stemming is done automatically.</li>
   </ul>
